Averaging samples from a population with log-normal distributionPublished on November 3, 2023 7:42 PM GMT<br/><br/><p>这最初是<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/users/mruwnik?from=post_header">Mruwnik</a>对<a href="https://www.lesswrong.com/posts/HjdqPbhRx2ceXHzr2/averages-and-sample-sizes">这篇文章</a>的评论，内容涉及平均具有不同分布的各种分布。我把它写成包含图片的帖子。</p><p>中心限制定理，此后CLT（用我自己的话来说）指出，无论人口的分布如何，该人群的样本平均值都应正态分布。</p><p>从理论上讲，它应该适用于对数正态分布，但这对我来说并不直观，所以我对其进行了测试。</p><h3> CLT的愚蠢例子</h3><p>我在脑海中构成的一个例子是为了理解它：</p><p>想象一个人口由所有一天中午睡2次的人组成。让我们绘制这个人群的年龄： </p><figure class="image image_resized" style="width:55.84%"><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/h8slnvin9v75wbh6vrww" srcset="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/m83kja1xoshnh65prhwn 158w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/c3n2ytq015maqwxq5jba 238w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/fnslxyz5ukg4nq5lbqnn 318w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/lhlkzjbmbklwjlcleskp 398w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/d0i6iip8afyolf7sojf5 478w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/flkvsioij0l7b0iy3fh0 558w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/m12rn0wnnl1qh1zwgkef 638w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/ora4h7hhuos4jwdjff40 718w, https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/GkEW4vH6M6pMdowdN/ui07ar9vidttgwmedksl 798w"></figure><p>大多是婴儿和老年人小睡，因此是图形的形状。这些数据不正常。但是，如果您从该人群中随机选择一个少量样本（n = 10），那么它将与平均中年的老年人和婴儿混合在一起。例